item.title: A New Beginning
item.description: To Study Design had always been a dream to me, now that I have completed Secondary Education, it is the right time to start my Higher Education and Specialisation.Design is now a globally acknowledged subject.From the beginning of man, although unintentionally he had been using simple design techniques to simplify his tasks.

item.title: A Refresh to indicator-stickynotes
item.description: I love good looking apps.As a budding UI designer, I should.I was a chronic user of Sticky Notes on Windows, when I had been a Windows User.Sticky Notes helped me save a lot of paper and got me to memorize my things in time.

item.title: Premam - A review by a novice
item.description: The new movie in town had been hitting hundreds all week long.Premam by Alphonse Putharen is not really a one-of-a-kind movie at all.But, it still packs a whole lot of punch in the package.It has something for everyone - and that is what makes the movie a real good one.
